    "question": "<p>Benda $A$ bermassa 2 satuan berada di koordinat (-1,2), sedangkan benda $B$ dengan massa 4 satuan berada di koordinat (2,-1). Di manakah posisi pusat massa sistem dua benda tersebut?</p>",
    "choices": [
        {
            "value": "0",
            "label": "(0,0)"
        },
        {
            "value": "1",
            "label": "(4,0)"
        },
        {
            "value": "2",
            "label": "(6,0)"
        },
        {
            "value": "3",
            "label": "(1,-4)"
        },
        {
            "value": "4",
            "label": "(1,-6)"
        }
    ],
    "answer": "5",
    "explain": "<p>Pusat massa sistem: ($x_{pm},y_{pm}$).\\\\ </p><p>$x_{pm}=\\frac{m_Ax_A+m_Bx_B}{m_A+m_B}=\\frac{-2+8}{6}=1$.\\\\ </p><p>$y_{pm}=\\frac{m_Ay_A+m_By_B}{m_A+m_B}=\\frac{4-4}{6}=0$.\\\\ </p><p>Koordinat pusat massa: (1,0)</p>"
}